children.subject: <md>I have the same question, but for 61B</md>

history.content:
Hello Everyone.

I was wondering if the current situation of COVID and what I once heard were budget cuts for departments will affect enrollment for CS61A during the adjustment period. I need to take another class during phase 2 and cannot take 61A also and was hoping that the waitlist wouldn't be cut short for 61A. Could anyone with more information on this respond? 

Thank you
